        <div id=item1>
            <h3 class="RainbowText GlitchHeader Mini">What is Skulk Space?</h3>
            <div id="item1-content" class="item-content">
                <p>Skulk Space is many things. At its heart, it is a shared identity for our community and a label under which we, Ergo and Vael, bring our creative visions to life.</p>
                <p>This website acts as a central hub, weaving together our diverse projects across multiple platforms, accounts, and community spaces. It's also a home for unique works—ranging from software and electronics to digital art and fiber creations—that don't fit within traditional mediums.</p>
                <P>Together, we are two multi-disciplinary artists, partners in life and creativity, who have been married since 2016. Skulk Space reflects our passion for storytelling, character design, and the endless pursuit of growth through art and exploration.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="item1-side">
