                <p>Vael is a 27-year-old multi-disciplinary Canadian artist specializing in digital and fiber arts. With a background in costume design, 3D modeling, and game design, her skills and interests extend well beyond her formal education.</p>
                <p>Driven by a passion for creativity and a determination to keep growing, Vael continually pushes the boundaries of her artistry.</p>
                <p>Explore the Gallery for examples of Vael's character designs, digital artworks, and sewing projects!</p>
                <h4>Aliases</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Vael</li>
