        </div>
        <div id=item3>
            <h3 class="RainbowText GlitchHeader Mini">About Ergo</h3>
            <div id="item3-content" class="item-content">
                <p>Ergo is a 28-year-old American-born artist and computer science student. In 2016, they immigrated to Canada to be with Vael and have lived there ever since, continuing their education in computing science.</p>
                <p>Ergo is passionate about story building and character design, which they bring to life through various mediums, including music, electronics, software, and, more recently, fabric arts.</p>
                <p>They believe that exploring diverse disciplines offers insights into both ourselves and the nature of art. Constantly driven to learn new skills, Ergo thrives on challenging themselves to uncover different facets of the human experience.</p>
